      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000047",
    "sentence": "是時，西鄙未寧，密邇寇境，鄩練兵撫眾，獨當一面。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000048",
    "sentence": "四年，加檢校太保、同平章事。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "四年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000049",
    "sentence": "庶人友珪篡位，加檢校太傅。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000050",
    "sentence": "乾化三年 正月，丁內艱，友珪命起復視事。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "三年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000051",
    "sentence": "未帝即位，尤深倚重。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000052",
    "sentence": "明年夏，詔鄩歸闕，授開封尹，遙領鎮南軍節度使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "遙領鎮",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 14,
        "end": 17
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000053",
    "sentence": "旋屬晉人寇河朔，鄩奉詔與魏節度使楊師厚禦之而退。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000054",
    "sentence": "九月，徐州節度使蔣殷據城叛。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "徐州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 3,
