      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000151",
    "sentence": "太祖受禪，加檢校太保。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_023_000152",
    "sentence": "開平元年 夏，命將大軍以伐潞州。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
